## 2. External Dependencies

This project uses various third-party libraries and build rules, including:
- Bazel (https://bazel.build/)
- rules_foreign_cc (https://github.com/bazel-contrib/rules_foreign_cc)
- rules_pkg (https://github.com/bazelbuild/rules_pkg)
- bazel_skylib (https://github.com/bazelbuild/bazel-skylib)
- rules_cc (https://github.com/bazelbuild/rules_cc)
- rules_python (https://github.com/bazelbuild/rules_python)
- rules_shell (https://github.com/bazelbuild/rules_shell)
- libtiff (http://www.libtiff.org/)
- X11 (https://www.x.org/)

Each of these dependencies is subject to its own license terms.
